data.Name: Matsumoto Zoku
data.Bio: Matsumoto Zoku is an alternative, organic music duo formed in 2013 in Melbourne. Originally from Japan, Matsumoto Zoku are based in Melbourne and Vienna. Koji Matsumoto plays Hand Pan and Didgeridoo. Reo Matsumoto is a Human Beat Maker, Hand Pan Player, Percussionist and Electronic musician. Matsumoto Zokuâ€™s career started on the streets of Melbourne. They are currently recording their Fifth album.
